#: includes/class-privacy.php:78
msgid "This data is stored locally on this site, deleted automatically after the configured retention period (30 days by default) and anonymised after 7 days by default. The legal basis is the operator's legitimate interest in the security and uninterrupted operation of the site (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR, Recital 49). User agents are not stored unless detailed logging is explicitly enabled."
